text: Chan Nyein Kyaw (; born 8 December 1992) is a Burmese footballer playing as a Goalkeeper for Burmese club Yadanarbon. He was signed from Rakhine United to the Yadanarbon. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:People from Yangon Region Category:Burmese footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Yadanarbon F.C. players
